    <data key="d0">Automated AWS Account Provisioning Engine</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Fd2c7NDYfpo</data>
    <data key="d2">A self-service platform for engineers to provision sandbox AWS accounts governed by Organizations, Service Control Policies, and budget-based teardowns.</data>
    <data key="d3">control, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
